	<h1 class="m-0 max-w-[900px] text-[clamp(2.35rem,5vw,4.9rem)] font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-normal">Agentic BDD/TDD Demo</h1>
	<p class="mb-0 mt-4 max-w-[760px] text-xl text-muted">
		A small ColdBox + BoxLang application for showing how executable behavior keeps
		AI-assisted code honest in a real Conference Session Review workflow.
	</p>
</section>

<section class="grid grid-cols-[minmax(180px,0.45fr)_1fr] gap-6 border-t border-line py-8 max-demo:block">
