	</div>
	<p class="m-0 text-[1.08rem] text-muted">
		The demo centers on realistic review rules: submissions must be complete, only eligible
		reviews count, thresholds are explicit, and final decisions stay traceable to the behavior
		the tests describe.
	</p>
</section>

